String.string: Wheels within wheels, my friends....you're still stumbling in the dark...no idea who's...really behind it all.
My death changes nothing. The argons will take you all!
Idiot! Live up to your promise. You shouldn't need reinforcements!
No! That was one of my most splendid creations! Your meddling ends now! Guards!
I can't watch this farce. Watch and learn, minions! Watch and learn how I deal with meddlers!
